title: Greyscale MobileNet [LB=0.892]
description: Keras MobileNet BenchmarkIn a previous benchmark we used a simple three layer ConvNet. This time we use a deeper MobileNet architecture on greyscale strokes. This kernel has three main components:  MobileNet Fast and memory efficient Image Generator with temporal colored strokes Full training & submission with Kaggle Kernel  I did some paramer search but it should not be hard to improve the current score.
